J. P. Lockney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._P._Lockney 0 J. P. Lockney (March 17, 1867, date of death unknown) was an American actor of the silent film era. He appeared in 105 films between 1915 and 1937. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. J._P._Lockney ( March_17_,_1867 , date of death_unknown ) was an_American_actor of the_silent_film_era .
